                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-77-off443 t18300708-77-cd444"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-77-off445 t18300708-77-cd444"></join> 4 bushels of bran, value 3s., and half a bushel of flour; value 6s., the goods of 
                     
