             was indicted for <rs id="t18300708-77-off445" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300708-77-off445" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300708-77-off445" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving the same, well knowing them to have been stolen, against the Statute
